# Dropbox should not sync generated / dependency / VCS artifacts.
# These stay on disk so the app builds & runs; they're recreated on demand
# (npm install / build / tests) and backed by GitHub — syncing them just
# thrashes Dropbox and causes red-X sync errors (65k+ locked files).
